---
---
<section id="creator" aria-labelledby="creator-heading">
  <div class="wrap cr-wrap">

    <!-- Big pull quote -->
    <div class="cr-quote-block" data-reveal>
      <svg class="crq-mark" viewBox="0 0 48 36" fill="none" aria-hidden="true">
        <path d="M0 36V22.5C0 10.1 7.2 3 21.6 0L24 4.2C17.4 6 14.1 9.6 14.4 15H22.8V36H0zM25.2 36V22.5C25.2 10.1 32.4 3 46.8 0L49.2 4.2C42.6 6 39.3 9.6 39.6 15H48V36H25.2z" fill="rgba(26,107,64,0.22)"/>
      </svg>
      <blockquote>
        <p class="crq-text">
          "I got tired of starting every AI conversation with a three-paragraph context dump.
          I was spending more time writing the setup than writing the actual work.
          PromptCraft started as a one-file Swift script. When it started saving me forty minutes a day,
          I turned it into a real app."
        </p>
        <footer class="crq-footer">
          <div class="crq-meta">
            <span class="crq-name">Oguzhan Atalay</span>
            <span class="crq-role mono">@oguzhnatly · Lisbon, Portugal</span>
          </div>
          <div id="creator-heading" class="crq-stats">
            <span><strong>265</strong> GitHub stars on flutter_carplay</span>
            <span><strong>12+</strong> products shipped</span>
            <span><strong>5+</strong> years full-stack engineering</span>
          </div>
        </footer>
      </blockquote>
    </div>

    <!-- Timeline + links -->
    <div class="cr-bottom" data-reveal data-d="2">
      <div class="cr-timeline">
        {[
          { when: '2024 Q1', what: 'First prototype — a menu bar app that prepended a role prompt to every request. One file of Swift. Worked immediately.' },
          { when: '2024 Q2', what: 'Added the style selector and context engine. Response quality was obviously better. Started showing it to other engineers.' },
          { when: '2024 Q4', what: 'Full 7-stage pipeline, clipboard history, and the cloud proxy for provider routing without API key management.' },
          { when: '2025',    what: 'Published. Still the only AI tool I actually keep open. Used every day, built on ever since.' },
        ].map(t => (
          <div class="cr-tl-row">
            <span class="cr-tl-when mono">{t.when}</span>
            <p class="cr-tl-what">{t.what}</p>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>

      <div class="cr-links">
        <a href="https://twitter.com/oguzhnatly" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="btn btn-ghost cr-link">
          <iconify-icon icon="simple-icons:x" style="font-size:13px;" aria-hidden="true"></iconify-icon>
          Follow the build
        </a>
        <a href="mailto:hello@promptcraft.app" class="btn btn-ghost cr-link">
          <iconify-icon icon="lucide:mail" style="font-size:13px;" aria-hidden="true"></iconify-icon>
          hello@promptcraft.app
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>

<style>
  #creator {
    padding: 72px 0 80px;
    background: var(--bg2);
    border-top: 1px solid var(--bdr); border-bottom: 1px solid var(--bdr);
  }

  .cr-wrap { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 56px; }

  /* Pull quote */
  .cr-quote-block { position: relative; padding-left: 0; }
  .crq-mark {
    width: 40px; height: 30px; margin-bottom: 20px; opacity: .7;
  }
  .crq-text {
    font-size: clamp(18px, 2.5vw, 26px);
    font-weight: 500; letter-spacing: -0.025em; line-height: 1.5;
    color: var(--ink2); max-width: 880px;
  }
  .crq-footer {
    display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 48px;
    margin-top: 28px; flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
  .crq-meta { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 4px; }
  .crq-name { font-size: 16px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: -0.02em; color: var(--ink); }
  .crq-role { font-size: 12px; color: var(--dim); }
  .crq-stats {
    display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 24px; flex-wrap: wrap;
    font-size: 13px; color: var(--mid);
  }
  .crq-stats strong { color: var(--ink); font-weight: 700; }

  /* Timeline */
  .cr-bottom { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 280px; gap: 64px; align-items: start; }
  .cr-timeline { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0; }
  .cr-tl-row {
    display: grid; grid-template-columns: 100px 1fr;
    gap: 24px; padding: 18px 0;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--bdr);
    align-items: start;
  }
  .cr-tl-row:last-child { border-bottom: 1px solid var(--bdr); }
  .cr-tl-when { font-size: 11px; font-weight: 600; color: var(--acc); letter-spacing: 0.04em; padding-top: 2px; }
  .cr-tl-what { font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.7; color: var(--mid); }

  .cr-links { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 8px; }
  .cr-link   { padding: 10px 18px; font-size: 13px; border-radius: 8px; }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .cr-bottom { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 32px; }
    .cr-links  { flex-direction: row; flex-wrap: wrap; }
  }
</style>
